name: Hill-View Bar and Restaurant

reviews.review_text:
The restaurant is tucked away in a serene and picturesque location, offering a perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of Goa. This is my personal favourite place, i visit this place every time when in goa.

The menu features a wide variety of Goan, Indian, and Continental dishes. The seafood is particularly fresh and flavorful, with standout dishes like the prawns curry, fish thali, lepo, modso and king fish. Their vegetarian options, such as the paneer tikka and vegetable biryani, are also excellent.

The flavors are rich and authentic, making every bite a treat for the taste buds.

Service is quick, worth it even if there is some waiting.  The restaurant offers stunning views of the surrounding hills and lush greenery. The first floor seating area is perfect for enjoying a meal while soaking in the natural beauty of Assagao.

Definitely a must visit place.

Had visited this place 10-12 years back. Was much smaller than, had better food and service. Always wanted to go back and finally when I got there last week it has totally changed in appearance. Seating has increased ten folds. The waiters seemed bored and talk to you in a transactional way. As it is the monsoon season, the variety of seafood available was very limited. We ordered chonak and it was fresh and tasty. Chicken and rice quantity was amazing. The bill was surprisingly low too. We were seated in the section that was more like a hut, also badly lit. However even after all this there were hordes of cars parked outside and people were rushing in even in the heavy down pour.

The Hill-View Bar and Restaurant Located in Xeldem, Curchorem locally know as "Annager" is a local Goan Restaurant. My friends and I visited this place on Sunday. They serve Goan Food at an affordable price. They have two seating areas one is upstairs which is for couple and family and other is on the ground floor for groups. They have a huge seating area. It's usually crowded during the weekends so the service is slow. They have a good parking area. It is recommended to visit early and give your order at one go and ask them to bring it one at a time. Taste wise food is good. I highly recommend Goan fish curry rice, tisreo and Chicken Tawa.

We ordered:
Tisreo
Chicken Sukka
Chicken Tawa
Chicken Tandoori
Rice Curry

Must visit place for Local Goan Food

description:
### Hill-View Bar and Restaurant: A Culinary Escape in Goa

Tucked away in the lush hills of Assagao, **Hill-View Bar and Restaurant** boasts an impressive rating of **4.2** from **1,304 reviews**, establishing itself as a favorite among both locals and travelers seeking authentic Goan cuisine. Regular patrons rave about the restaurant's specialties, with tags such as **“Goan”** (55 reviews), **“thali”** (19), and **“fish curry”** (12) reflecting a strong emphasis on local flavors. 

### Ambiance & Design

As you step inside Hill-View, you are greeted by stunning views of the surrounding greenery, making it a serene escape from the bustling beaches of Goa. The restaurant features a spacious layout with two main seating areas: an intimate upstairs space ideal for couples and families, and a lively ground floor that accommodates larger groups. The décor is rustic yet cozy, adorned with warm lighting that complements the nature-themed surroundings. Highlights from customer-provided photos showcase a charming hut-like structure, inviting you to unwind as you indulge in your meal. 

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Hill-View is a delightful journey through Goan, Indian, and Continental dishes. Customers consistently highlight the freshness and flavor of the seafood, with personal favorites including the **prawns curry**, **fish thali**, and **king fish**. Vegetarians can savor the delicious **paneer tikka** and aromatic **vegetable biryani**, ensuring there's something for everyone. The presentation of the dishes is equally commendable, with vibrant colors and meticulous plating that tantalize the taste buds before the first bite. Each review speaks to the authentic flavors that define Goan cuisine, providing a genuine taste of the region.

### Customer Experience & Service

While most diners agree that the service is generally quick and efficient, some have noted variability, especially during peak hours when the restaurant is crowded. One reviewer mentioned the importance of ordering early and in one go to ensure a smoother experience. Although a couple of guests had mixed feelings about the service — with one describing it as "transactional" — many emphasize that the flavors and views more than make up for any minor lapses in service quality. The restaurant's casual vibe encourages a relaxed dining experience where guests can soak in the natural beauty surrounding them. 

### Popularity & Reviews

Hill-View Bar and Restaurant has carved out a significant reputation, with consistent media buzz and social media mentions that reinforce its status as a must-visit spot in Goa. The overwhelmingly positive sentiments expressed in customer reviews showcase a collaborative appreciation for its culinary offerings and the atmospheric charm it provides. Many paid homage to the restaurant's ability to deliver authentic Goan flavors at wallet-friendly prices, making it an accessible option for all.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Visual content accompanying the reviews reveals much about the restaurant's ambiance and food presentation. Photographs depict cozy, inviting interiors bathed in soft lighting and mouthwatering dishes that look as delectable as they taste. Highlights include beautifully plated fish curry and the bustling dining area filled with diners enjoying their meals amidst the enchanting surroundings.

### Conclusion

In summary, **Hill-View Bar and Restaurant** is not just a place to dine but an experience that immerses you in the essence of Goa’s culinary heritage. Whether you’re indulging in your favorite **fish thali** or enjoying the views from the first-floor seating, this restaurant promises a memorable dining adventure. So, if you find yourself in Goa, take a moment to relax and enjoy the tranquility offered by this hidden gem.
